title: Harvey Weinstein gives Hollywood's and Washington's names, the child-enemy to the FBI?
subtitle: According to reports, the movie-fighter producer about "the names of the pedophile elite" in Hollywood and Washington, D.C., is bogus news.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Movie producer Harvey Weinstein made a deal with the FBI to hand over "the names of selected child molesters in Hollywood and Washington, D.C.."
